Package: wpscan
Version: 4.0.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: ruby, ruby-nokogiri, ruby-ethon, libcurl, libffi, sed, findutils
Section: web
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://wpscan.com/
Description: WordPress vulnerability scanner
 WPScan is a security scanner for WordPress websites, built with
 an extensive vulnerability database. It identifies themes, plugins,
 and core issues, and provides actionable security reports.
